  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    org.numenta.nupic.Parameters.getMap()
    Will have private access, replaced by Parameters.setParameterByKey(KEY, Object). Need it to to be compatible with EnumMap p = parameters.getMap() in tests. Creates and returns an EnumMap containing the specified keys; whose values are to be loaded later. The map returned is only created if the internal reference is null (never been created), therefore the map is a singleton which cannot be recreated once created.
